vzlicload 
^^^^^^^^^
 
Installs and removes Virtuozzo licenses.
  
.Syntax
[subs="quotes"]
----
vzlicload [-p, --product-key _&lt;key&gt;_ | -f, --license-file _&lt;file_path&gt;_]
          [-r, --remove] [-i, --stdin] [-h, --help]
----
  
.Options
[options="header",cols="1a,3a"]
|====
|Name|Description

|+-p, --product-key _&lt;key&gt;_+|Installs the specified Virtuozzo license on the server.
|+-f, --license-file _&lt;file_path&gt;_+|The full path to the license file containing the license to be installed on the server.
|`-r, --remove`|Removes the license with the specified serial number from the server. You can find out the license serial number using the `vzlicview` utility.
|`-i, --stdin`|Makes `vzlicload` use standard input as a license.
|`-h, --help`|Prints the usage help and exits.
